Enum MultextPartOfSpeech

  • java.lang.Object
    • java.lang.Enum<MultextPartOfSpeech>
      • it.jrc.lt.core.component.morphology.MultextPartOfSpeech
  • All Implemented Interfaces:

    public enum MultextPartOfSpeech
extends java.lang.Enum<MultextPartOfSpeech>
    This class contains all part-of-speech categories used in MULTEXT. Each of them is accompanied with a list of appropriate feature names
    Author:
    Jakub Piskorski
